    // in production, the widget would likely be a <section> or <asside> element of it's own.
    .widget-container
      header.widget-header
        h1 Your Electricity Savings
      section.widget-content
        .widget-visual
          p visual goes here
          ul.widget-button-group
            li: a.widget-button Cars
            li: a.widget-button Trees
            li: a.widget-button C02
        .widget-data
          h2 Last month, you saved enough energy to take six cars off the road!
          p Great job! You used 573 kWH last month, compared to 791 kWh in the same month last year. The resulting savings is enough to offset the energy consumption of six average-size cars for one month.



